distance between the whole steps

00:58:41.220 --> 00:58:43.220
and half steps in the scale.

00:58:43.220 --> 00:58:47.830
So the actual frequency
difference, in today's standard,

00:58:47.830 --> 00:58:50.200
is called equal temperament tuning,

00:58:50.200 --> 00:58:53.500
which means in between every
half step is the same number

00:58:53.500 --> 00:58:56.120
of frequencies, in
between each half step.

00:58:56.120 --> 00:58:58.410
In the seventeenth century,

00:58:58.410 --> 00:59:03.340
and in most times before
the nineteenth century,

00:59:03.340 --> 00:59:06.950
