from one or 2 sharps or, you know,

00:59:49.010 --> 00:59:54.460
what have you, then it became
more and more dissonant.

00:59:54.460 --> 00:59:56.010
And so the idea of dissonance

00:59:56.010 --> 01:00:00.290
