don't really tend to understand

01:00:02.890 --> 01:00:07.460
because it's not only a half step
next to each other being dissonant,

01:00:07.460 --> 01:00:12.180
but a half step that
is tuned differently.

01:00:12.180 --> 01:00:15.990
Being closer together
possibly or further away,

01:00:15.990 --> 01:00:18.690
in frequency that sounds
much more dissonant

01:00:18.690 --> 01:00:21.620
than if you just play two notes
next to each other on a piano.

01:00:21.620 --> 01:00:26.030
